<function>

access:   public

name: fetch

param: Solar_Sql_Table, $table

param: array, $list, '*'

param: string, $array_name, NULL

return: Solar_Form|false

</function>

Loads Solar_Form elements based on Solar_Sql_Table columns.

* Parameters:

 * Solar_Sql_Table //$table//: Load form elements from this table object.

 * array //$list//: Which table columns to load as form elements, default '*'.

 * string //$array_name//: Load the table columns as elements of this array-name within the form.

* Returns Solar_Form|false: Solar_Form object, or boolean false on error.

Loads Solar_Form elements based on Solar_Sql_Table columns.